---
import Accordion from "../../../components/accordion.astro";
import TabbedDialog from "../../../components/tabbed-dialog.astro";
---

<section
  class="bg-[url(/images/why-messiah-bg-grad.jpg)] bg-no-repeat bg-cover py-24 relative scroll-m-24"
  id="why-messiah"
>
  <div class="wrapper" x-data="{ selected: null }">
    <h2 class="text-white h2 text-center">Why Messiah?</h2>
    <p class="text-white text-center paragraph mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      Messiah’s graduate programs are designed to challenge your intellect, engage your faith and
      fit your busy lifestyle.
    </p>

    <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 my-16">
      <li>
        <button
          @click="selected = 'index-0'"
          type="button"
          class="text-white group font-title w-full font-bold text-center text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl flex flex-col items-center"
        >
          <img
            src="https://www.messiah.edu/site/custom_scripts/styles/img/academics/academic-excellence-circle.png"
            alt=""
            class="mb-2 rounded-full group-hover:opacity-75 transition-opacity"
          />
          Completely overpriced
        </button>
      </li>
      <li>
        <button
          @click="selected = 'index-1'"
          type="button"
          class="text-white group font-title w-full font-bold text-center text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl flex flex-col items-center"
        >
          <img
            src="https://www.messiah.edu/site/custom_scripts/styles/img/academics/competitively-priced-circle-2.png"
            alt=""
            class="mb-2 rounded-full group-hover:opacity-75 transition-opacity"
          />
          Academic excellence
        </button>
      </li>
      <li>
        <button
          @click="selected = 'index-2'"
          type="button"
          class="text-white group font-title w-full font-bold text-center text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl flex flex-col items-center"
        >
          <img
            src="https://www.messiah.edu/site/custom_scripts/styles/img/academics/faith-commitment-circle.png"
            alt=""
            class="mb-2 rounded-full group-hover:opacity-75 transition-opacity"
          />
          Faith commitment
        </button>
      </li>
      <li>
        <button
          @click="selected = 'index-3'"
          type="button"
          class="text-white group font-title w-full font-bold text-center text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl flex flex-col items-center"
        >
          <img
            src="https://www.messiah.edu/site/custom_scripts/styles/img/academics/exceptional-faculty-circle.png"
            alt=""
            class="mb-2 rounded-full group-hover:opacity-75 transition-opacity"
          />
          Exceptional faculty
        </button>
      </li>
      <li>
        <button
          @click="selected = 'index-4'"
          type="button"
          class="text-white group font-title w-full font-bold text-center text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl flex flex-col items-center"
        >
          <img
            src="https://www.messiah.edu/site/custom_scripts/styles/img/academics/flexible-class-circle.png"
            alt=""
            class="mb-2 rounded-full group-hover:opacity-75 transition-opacity"
          />
          Flexible class formats
        </button>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <TabbedDialog
      tabs={[
        { name: "Completely overpriced" },
        { name: "Academic excellence" },
        { name: "Faith commitment" },
        { name: "Exceptional faculty" },
        { name: "Flexible class formats" },
      ]}
      title="Why Messiah?"
      class="bg-[url(/images/why-messiah-bg-grad.jpg)] bg-no-repeat bg-cover bg-primary-950"
    >
      <div
        id="tabbed-dialog-tabpanel-0"
        role="tabpanel"
        x-show="selected === 'index-0'"
        aria-labelledby="tabbed-dialog-tab-0"
      >
        <h4
          class="text-center text-3xl my-12 relative before:absolute before:w-1/4 md:before:w-1/4 before:h-1 before:bg-gray-400 before:left-0 before:top-1/2 after:absolute after:w-1/4 md:after:w-1/4 after:h-1 after:bg-gray-400 after:right-0 after:top-1/2 after:hidden before:hidden md:after:block md:before:block"
        >
          Competitively priced
        </h4>

        <img
          src="https://www.messiah.edu/site/custom_scripts/styles/img/academics/academic-excellence.jpg"
          alt=""
          class="float-right ml-4 mb-4 w-1/3"
        />

        <p class="mb-4 paragraph">
          Messiah University strives to keep our graduate programs competitively priced and
          accessible, and we offer a variety of financial aid and discount opportunities to our
          graduate students. Types of aid available include student loans, student employment,
          grants, private scholarships, veterans’ benefits, graduate programs discounts and employer
          assistance.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-4 paragraph">
          No-fee tuition<br />
          At Messiah University, most of our graduate programs feature no-fee tuition. The cost per credit
          is what you pay–there are no hidden fees for labs, courses, services or technology. We put
          the true cost of your program upfront so that you can accurately compare and plan for your
          graduate education.
        </p>

        <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap mt-4">
          <a
            class="btn-quaternary"
            href="https://www.messiah.edu/info/21313/financial_aid_for_graduate_programs"
            >Financial aid</a
          >
          <a class="btn-quaternary" href="https://www.messiah.edu/info/22941/tuition_and_fees"
            >Tuition</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        id="tabbed-dialog-tabpanel-1"
        role="tabpanel"
        x-show="selected === 'index-1'"
        aria-labelledby="tabbed-dialog-tab-1"
      >
        <h4
          class="text-center text-3xl my-12 relative before:absolute before:w-1/4 md:before:w-1/4 before:h-1 before:bg-gray-400 before:left-0 before:top-1/2 after:absolute after:w-1/4 md:after:w-1/4 after:h-1 after:bg-gray-400 after:right-0 after:top-1/2 after:hidden before:hidden md:after:block md:before:block"
        >
          Academic excellence
        </h4>

        <img
          src="https://www.messiah.edu/site/custom_scripts/styles/img/academics/competitively-priced-modal.jpg"
          alt=""
          class="float-right ml-4 mb-4 w-1/3"
        />

        <p class="mb-4 paragraph">
          Messiah University successfully integrates top-tier academics and Christian faith. To meet
          the need of working professionals, our curriculum and coursework is designed to be
          instantly relevant to your career.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        id="tabbed-dialog-tabpanel-2"
        role="tabpanel"
        x-show="selected === 'index-2'"
        aria-labelledby="tabbed-dialog-tab-2"
      >
        <h4
          class="text-center text-3xl my-12 relative before:absolute before:w-1/4 md:before:w-1/4 before:h-1 before:bg-gray-400 before:left-0 before:top-1/2 after:absolute after:w-1/4 md:after:w-1/4 after:h-1 after:bg-gray-400 after:right-0 after:top-1/2 after:hidden before:hidden md:after:block md:before:block"
        >
          Faith commitment
        </h4>

        <img
          src="https://www.messiah.edu/site/custom_scripts/styles/img/academics/faith-commitment.jpg"
          alt=""
          class="float-right ml-4 mb-4 w-1/3"
        />

        <p class="mb-4 paragraph">
          Messiah University is a Christian university of the liberal and applied arts and sciences
          with a mission of educating men and women for lives of service, leadership and
          reconciliation. As a graduate student, you will be called to view your career and
          education through the lens of faith as you experience our distinct Christian and
          values-based education.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        id="tabbed-dialog-tabpanel-3"
        role="tabpanel"
        x-show="selected === 'index-3'"
        aria-labelledby="tabbed-dialog-tab-3"
      >
        <h4
          class="text-center text-3xl my-12 relative before:absolute before:w-1/4 md:before:w-1/4 before:h-1 before:bg-gray-400 before:left-0 before:top-1/2 after:absolute after:w-1/4 md:after:w-1/4 after:h-1 after:bg-gray-400 after:right-0 after:top-1/2 after:hidden before:hidden md:after:block md:before:block"
        >
          Exceptional faculty
        </h4>

        <img
          src="https://www.messiah.edu/site/custom_scripts/styles/img/academics/exceptional-faculty.jpg"
          alt=""
          class="float-right ml-4 mb-4 w-1/3"
        />

        <p class="mb-4 paragraph">
          Our faculty creates a stimulating learning environment that will challenge and advance you
          in your area of expertise. Courses are taught by Messiah University faculty, who are
          effective Christian educators, practicing professionals, outstanding scholars,
          researchers, authors and sought-after experts in their fields.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        id="tabbed-dialog-tabpanel-4"
        role="tabpanel"
        x-show="selected === 'index-4'"
        aria-labelledby="tabbed-dialog-tab-4"
      >
        <h4
          class="text-center text-3xl my-12 relative before:absolute before:w-1/4 md:before:w-1/4 before:h-1 before:bg-gray-400 before:left-0 before:top-1/2 after:absolute after:w-1/4 md:after:w-1/4 after:h-1 after:bg-gray-400 after:right-0 after:top-1/2 after:hidden before:hidden md:after:block md:before:block"
        >
          Flexible class formats
        </h4>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <p class="sm:w-3/4 paragraph">
            The majority of Messiah University’s graduate courses are conducted primarily online;
            however, some programs are fully online, others offer a hybrid format that combines
            online courses with several weeklong on-campus sessions, and a couple are full-time
            traditional programs.
          </p>

          <img
            src="https://www.messiah.edu/site/custom_scripts/styles/img/academics/flexible-class.jpg"
            alt=""
            class="w-full sm:w-1/4 self-start"
          />
        </div>

        <Accordion transparent title="Traditional" class="mt-8">
          <h4 class="h4 mb-4">Traditional</h4>
          <p class="paragraph mb-4">
            Students meet at a physical location during scheduled meeting times for the duration of
            the course.
          </p>

          <p class="paragraph mb-4">
            The following graduate programs are offered in a traditional format:
          </p>

          <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
            <li>Occupational therapy</li>
            <li>Physical therapy</li>
          </ul>
        </Accordion>

        <Accordion transparent title="Hybrid">
          <h4 class="h4 mb-4">Hybrid</h4>
          <p class="paragraph mb-4">
            Most of Messiah’s graduate programs are conducted in a hybrid format which combines
            face-to-face meetings and online delivery.
          </p>

          <p class="paragraph mb-4">
            The following graduate programs are offered in a hybrid format:
          </p>

          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
            <li>Counseling</li>
            <li>Education *</li>
            <li>Higher education</li>
            <li>Music conducting</li>
            <li>Nursing</li>
            <li>Dietetic internship</li>
          </ul>

          <p>
            * Students who pursue the PDE certification in special education (PreK-8 or 7-12) as a
            part of the M.Ed. degree or as a non-degree option must come to campus for some one-week
            intensive courses. All other education graduate programs can be completed entirely
            online.
          </p>
        </Accordion>

        <Accordion transparent title="Online">
          <h4 class="h4 mb-4">Online</h4>
          <p class="paragraph mb-4">
            Students access all course materials online through a learning management system: there
            are no requirements for face-to-face sessions.
          </p>

          <p class="paragraph mb-4">
            The following graduate programs are offered in an online format:
          </p>

          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
            <li>Business and leadership</li>
            <li>Education *</li>
          </ul>

          <p>
            * Students who pursue the PDE certification in special education (PreK-8 or 7-12) as a
            part of the M.Ed. degree or as a non-degree option must come to campus for some one-week
            intensive courses. All other education graduate programs can be completed entirely
            online.
          </p>
        </Accordion>

        <div class="flex gap-4 flex-wrap mt-8 justify-center">
          <a
            class="btn-quaternary"
            href="https://www.messiah.edu/info/22871/program_and_class_format"
            >Learn more about Messiah's Graduate class formats</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </TabbedDialog>
  </div>
</section>
